    "updated_at": "2015-07-28T08:25:03Z",
    "body": "The modification I made is only in [code for OSX ](https://github.com/atom/electron/blob/master/atom/browser/ui/cocoa/atom_menu_controller.mm), so other platforms aren't affected. I have also documented this in the section for building menus on OS X, which already mentions those specal menus.\n"
